TITLE: Triggering Actions on Sunrise (Java DSL)
DESCRIPTION: This Java DSL snippet defines a rule that raises blinds and adjusts temperature when the sun rises. It uses the Astro Binding's channel event to trigger the actions.
SOURCE: https://github.com/openhab/openhab-docs/blob/main/concepts/rules.md#2025-04-09_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: java
CODE:
```
rule "Raise the blinds & adjust temperature on sunrise"
when
  Channel 'astro:sun:home:rise#event' triggered START
then
  gBlinds.sendCommand(UP)
  gThermostat.sendCommand(INCREASE)
end
```

