TITLE: Adding openHAB Repository Key on apt-based Systems
DESCRIPTION: Commands to add the openHAB repository key to package manager on Debian-based systems. This creates the necessary GPG key configuration for secure package verification.
SOURCE: https://github.com/openhab/openhab-docs/blob/main/installation/linux.md#2025-04-09_snippet_0

